# To-Do List API

A simple in-memory CRUD REST API for managing tasks, built with FastAPI.

## Endpoints

| Method | URL | Description |
|--------|-----|-------------|
| GET | `/` | API status |
| GET | `/tasks` | Get all tasks |
| GET | `/tasks/{id}` | Get one task |
| POST | `/tasks` | Create task |
| PATCH | `/tasks/{id}/done` | Mark as done |
| DELETE | `/tasks/{id}` | Delete task |

## Run locally
```bash
docker build -t todo-api .
docker run -p 8000:8000 todo-api
```

Visit `http://localhost:8000/docs` for interactive docs.

## CI/CD Pipeline

GitHub Actions workflow that builds the image, pushes to ghcr.io, and runs Docker Scout CVE scanning.